# LLM gateway keys — only needed for the `critique` / `eval` features
# (install with `vizier[critique]`). The computable toolkit
# (validate / suggest-palette / suggest-ramp / recommend-form / analyze / ink)
# needs NONE of these.
#
# Copy to `.env` and fill in what you have. vizier routes LLM calls through `somm`;
# each provider is opt-in via its key.

GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional additional providers somm can route to:
# MINIMAX_API_KEY=
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
